images are not obliged to, but linking to their site will be highly
appreciated. So I decided to make a post plus show how people can link
sites at

http://bloggerfordummies.blogspot.com/2007/07/how-you-can-help-blogge...

and also say readers are not obliged but linking will be appreciated.
BTW will welcome feedback from you guys what is your reaction when you
get a message like this. Do you feel offended or something similar, or
feel the person asking for the link is too much

I get lots of requests for help in comments in my blogs plus email and
sometimes add a signature line like

Peter (Blog*Star)
http://bloggerfordummies.blogspot.com/2007/07/how-you-can-help-blogge...
(no one should feel obligated. Everthing completely voluntary.
However, by doing so, you may also help your visitors find helpful
information and help. You may even pick up various ways of linking
sites there too)

and then leave readers to decide for themself without persuasions.

BTW I am getting too many requests for help to the extend I find it
difficult to manage my own blogs plus other tasks and now weighting
getting an autoresponder to tell them I cannot cope and suggests ways
they can find posts in my blogs that can help them, and maybe answer
